These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, parkour
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | parkour | lacrosse | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, spinach, plum
1. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | kiwi | plum | spinach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | card-games | gardening | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, reggae, salsa
1. the fan of reggae is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | salsa | reggae |

