.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, puzzles, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby   | puzzles | video-games | hiking |

 